bdglue2.source.gghadoop

Class GG12HandlerMapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • bdglue2.source.gghadoop.GG12HandlerMapper

  • public class GG12HandlerMapper
extends Object
    This class essentially takes care of mapping the classes that are defined and used by the GoldenGate Java Adapter to the classes that are used by BDGlue. The intent is to completely decouple the two sides to hopefully make it easier to change as the GoldenGate Java API evolves.
